139
00:08:56,159 --> 00:08:57,919
Luring naive workplace newcomers.

140
00:08:58,039 --> 00:08:59,399
Using photos to blackmail them into serving me.

141
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,360
Everything you did back then...

142
